		<td><b>Game novelizations</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Do you know of any novelizations of old games?<br />I'm not talking about general stories with Mario, Mega Man or whoever in it, but about stories that are actually a novelization conversion of a specific game's plot.<br />Like if there was a book that tells the story of Trevor Belmont how he sets out to defeat Dracula and meets Alucard, Sypha and Grant on the way. That's what I'm looking for.<br />On the other hand, a story about how Trevor and Sypha, who are now married, fight a group of vampires that try to kill them because they defeated Dracula three years ago, that's not what I want.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


