	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Elite is perhaps the most famous for this. Wikipedia even says it was the first video game with a novel included.<br /><br />I also recall a fiction book from late 1990s that was loosely based on UFO: Enemy Unknown. Not sure if it was licensed, though, but it was published as a normal book, with good print quality, hardcover etc.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


